    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Inlet Air Heater</title>
        <para>The inlet air heater feature improves engine start-up in cold weather. The ECM controls the intake air
            heater and monitors the engine temperature. When the engine is ready for cranking, the ECM sends a message
            to shut off the WAIT TO START lamp.
        </para>
        <para>For additional information, see
            <hotlnk document="eges270_148.xml" xrefid="IAH">"IAH System"</hotlnk>
            in Section 7 .
        </para>
    </svcproc>
